# Project Structure & Navigation

Use this as a quick map of the repo. Key files are linked for quick-open.

- Workspace: [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml)
- Root TS config: [tsconfig.base.json](mdc:tsconfig.base.json)
- Lint/format: [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs), [.prettierrc.json](mdc:.prettierrc.json)
- Versioning: [.changeset/config.json](mdc:.changeset/config.json)
- Tasks backlog: [TASKS.md](mdc:TASKS.md)
- PRD: [PRD.md](mdc:PRD.md)

Packages (workspace/*):

- Core engine: [packages/core](mdc:packages/core)
- React/Next adapter: [packages/adapter-react-next](mdc:packages/adapter-react-next)
- Vue/Nuxt adapter (stub): [packages/adapter-vue-nuxt](mdc:packages/adapter-vue-nuxt)
- CLI: [packages/cli](mdc:packages/cli)

Build:

- Package build: run `pnpm -r build`
- Individual: run `pnpm dev` inside a package
